  <brief_title>Study of Vitamin D3 Substitution to Patients With Primary Immunodeficiency</brief_title>
  <acronym>VITAPID</acronym>
  <official_title>A Placebo Controlled Double Blinded Study of Vitamin D3 Substitution to Patients With Primary Immunodeficiency</official_title>
